text: Mika Sue Boorem (born August 18, 1987) is an American actress. She acts in both movies and television. She was in Carolina (2003) and Blue Crush in 2002. Boorem was born in Tucson, Arizona. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Tucson, Arizona
